properties.name: DraughtLevel
properties.documentation: The measure of the draught level of this logistics means of transport.

properties.name: ForwardDraughtLevel
properties.documentation: The draught level measured at the fore end of this transport means.

properties.name: AftDraughtLevel
properties.documentation: The draught level measured at the aft end of this transport means.

properties.name: Helipad
properties.documentation: The indication of whether or not there is a helipad on this logistics means of transport.

properties.name: ManoeuvringSpeed
properties.documentation: The manoeuvring speed measured for this logistics means of transport.

ownedElements.name: VoyageLifecycle
ownedElements.documentation: The state lifecycle of a trasnport movement

properties.name: PilotageExemption
properties.documentation: The identifier of a pilotage exemption for this logistics transport movement.

properties.name: SailingAdviceNotificationInformation
properties.documentation: Sailing advice notification information, expressed as text, for this logistics transport movement.

properties.name: DriverAccompanied
properties.documentation: The indication of whether or not this logistics means of transport is accompanied by a driver.

ownedElements.name: TransportEvent
CertifyingTradeParty
ownedElements.documentation: A certifying party for this transport event.

ownedElements.name: RelatedLocation
ownedElements.documentation: The location of a conveyance facility related to this transport event.

ownedElements.name: EventLocation
ownedElements.documentation: The logistics location where this transport event occurs.

ownedElements.name: RelatedTransportRoute
ownedElements.documentation: The route related to this transport event.
A significant occurrence or happening during transport.

properties.name: Type
properties.documentation: The code specifying the type of transport event.

properties.name: OccurrenceTime
properties.documentation: The actual date, time, date time, or other date time value of the occurrence of this transport event.

properties.name: ReportedTime
properties.documentation: The date, time, date time or other date time value of the actual arrival related to this transport event.

properties.name: Description
properties.documentation: The textual description of this transport event.

ownedElements.name: TransportMovement
ActualEvent
ownedElements.documentation: A transport event specified for this logistics transport movement.

ownedElements.name: UsedTransportMeans
ownedElements.documentation: The means of transport used for this logistics transport movement.
The conveyance (physical carriage) of goods or other objects used for logistics transport purposes.

properties.name: Identification
properties.documentation: The unique identifier for this logistics transport movement, such as a voyage number, flight number, or trip number.

properties.name: TerminalOperatorAssignedIdentification
properties.documentation: A unique identifier for this logistics transport movement as assigned by a terminal operator.

properties.name: Stay
properties.documentation: The unique identifier of a stay in a port, airport or other place of service for this logistics transport movement.

properties.name: Status
properties.documentation: The code specifying a status for the logistics transport movement, such as estimated or final.

properties.name: Mode
properties.documentation: The code specifying the mode, such as by air, sea, rail, road or inland waterway, for this logistics transport movement.

properties.name: Stage
properties.documentation: The code specifying the stage of this logistics transport movement.

properties.name: CargoDescription
properties.documentation: The textual description of the cargo for this logistics transport movement.

properties.name: Closing
properties.documentation: The date, time, date time, or other date time value by which cargo should be loaded onto the means of transport for the departure of this logistics transport movement.

properties.name: Information
properties.documentation: Information, expressed as text, for this logistics transport movement.

properties.name: DangerousGoods
properties.documentation: The indication of whether or not dangerous goods are carried for this logistics transport movement.

properties.name: ManifestOnboard
properties.documentation: The indication of whether or not the manifest for this logistics transport movement is onboard.

properties.name: TransitDirection
properties.documentation: The code specifying the transit direction of this logistics transport movement.

properties.name: TransportEquipment
properties.documentation: The number of pieces of transport equipment for this logistics transport movement.

properties.name: Package
properties.documentation: The number of packages in this logistics transport movement.

properties.name: Consignment
properties.documentation: The number of consignments in this logistics transport movement.

properties.name: Crew
properties.documentation: The number of crew members for this logistics transport movement.

properties.name: Passenger
properties.documentation: The number of passengers for this logistics transport movement.

ownedElements.name: LogisticsLocation
PostalTradeAddress
ownedElements.documentation: The postal trade address information for this logistics related location.
A logistics related physical location or place.

properties.name: OtherIdentification
properties.documentation: A unique identifier for this logistics related location, such as a United Nations Location Code (UNLOCODE) or GS1 Global Location Number (GLN).

properties.name: Name
properties.documentation: A name, expressed as text, of this logistics related location.

properties.name: Description
properties.documentation: A textual description of this logistics related location.

properties.name: Country
properties.documentation: The unique identifier of a country for this logistics location.

properties.name: Type
properties.documentation: A code specifying the type of this logistics related location.

ownedElements.name: TransportMeans
RegistrationTransportEvent
ownedElements.documentation: A registration event of this logistics transport means.
The devices used to convey goods or other objects from place to place during logistics cargo movements.

properties.name: Identification
properties.documentation: An identifier of this logistics means of transport, such as the International Maritime Organization number of a vessel.

properties.name: Name
properties.documentation: The name, expressed as text, of this logistics means of transport.

properties.name: CargoGrossWeight
properties.documentation: The measure of the total gross weight (mass) of all cargo loaded onto this logistics means of transport, including packaging but excluding any associated transport equipment.

properties.name: Conference
properties.documentation: The code specifying the conference for this logistics means of transport.

properties.name: GrossWeight
properties.documentation: The measure of the gross weight (mass) of this logistics means of transport including cargo, such as the measure of the overall size of a vessel determined in accordance with the provisions of the International Convention on Tonnage Measurement of Ships, 1969.

properties.name: ISPSSecurityLevel
properties.documentation: The code specifying the International Ship and Port facility Security (ISPS) level assigned to this logistics means of transport.

properties.name: Length
properties.documentation: The measure of the length of this logistics means of transport.

properties.name: LoadedCargo
properties.documentation: The measure of the cargo loaded onto this logistics means of transport, such as the number of barrels of oil or other quantity of breakbulk cargo.

properties.name: NetWeight
properties.documentation: The measure of the net weight (mass) of this logistics means of transport, such as the net tonnage of a vessel determined in accordance with the provisions of the International Convention on Tonnage Measurement of Ships, 1969.

properties.name: RequiredLaneLength
properties.documentation: The measure of the external length required in a lane for this logistics transport means.

properties.name: Sequence
properties.documentation: The sequence number differentiating this logistics transport means from others.

properties.name: Type
properties.documentation: The code specifying the type of logistics means of transport (Reference UNECE Recommendation 28).

properties.name: TypeText
properties.documentation: The type, expressed as text, of this logistics means of transport.

properties.name: WasteReportingExemption
properties.documentation: The indication of whether or not there is a waste reporting exemption for this logistics means of transport.

ownedElements.name: TransportRoute
ItineraryStopLocation
ownedElements.documentation: An itinerary stop event for this transport route, such as a port call in a vessel schedule.
A way or course taken from one location to another for the purpose of transporting cargo and or passengers.

properties.name: Identification
properties.documentation: The unique identifier of this transport route.

properties.name: DeparturePoint
properties.documentation: A departure point, expressed as text, for this transport route.

properties.name: Description
properties.documentation: The textual description of this transport route.

properties.name: FrequencyType
properties.documentation: The code specifying the type of frequency for this transport route, such as weekly, bi-monthly or daily.

properties.name: Map
properties.documentation: Binary object data that is the map of this transport route.

properties.name: Status
properties.documentation: The code specifying a status for a transport route, such as planned or actual.

properties.name: TransportMeans
properties.documentation: A means of transport, expressed as text, for this transport route.
